*[[1903]] &amp;ndash; [[Edmond Nocard]], French veterinarian and biologist (b. 1850)
*[[1913]] &amp;ndash; [[Ferenc Pfaff]], Hungarian architect, designed [[Zagreb Central Station]] (b. 1851)
*[[1920]] &amp;ndash; [[Ormer Locklear]], American pilot (b. 1891)
*[[1921]] &amp;ndash; [[Enrico Caruso]], Italian tenor (b. 1873)
