*[[1945]] &amp;ndash; [[Pietro Mascagni]], Italian composer (b. 1863)
*[[1951]] &amp;ndash; [[John Paine (sport shooter)|John Paine]], American target shooter (b. 1870)
*[[1955]] &amp;ndash; [[Alfred Lépine]], Canadian ice hockey player (b. 1901)
*[[1967]] &amp;ndash; [[Walter Terence Stace]], English philosopher (b. 1886)
